From: majianpeng <majianpeng@gmail.com>
Subject: raid1: Add a field array_frozen to indicate whether raid in freeze state.
Patch-mainline: v13.3-rc1
Git-commit: b364e3d048e49b1d177eb7ee7853e77aa0560464
References: FATE#315669
    
    Because the following patch will rewrite the content between normal IO
    and resync IO. So we used a parameter to indicate whether raid is in freeze
    array.
    
Signed-off-by: Jianpeng Ma <majianpeng@gmail.com>
Signed-off-by: NeilBrown <neilb@suse.de>
Acked-by: Shirish Pargaonkar <spargaonkar@suse.com>
---
